Businesses should promote inclusive growth and equitable development:
Globalization and technological progress have led to rapid economic growth, but the resultant advantages have not been equally distributed. We seek to rectify this disparity by addressing heightened economic and social instability, as well as global challenges. We prioritize embedding Inclusive Growth into vital business choices, providing a framework for both our company and investors.
